# --- Secrets / licenses (NEVER commit) ---
*.license
*Splunk*.lic
*.lic
.env
.env.*
secrets.json
**/local/          # Splunk local/ dirs hold instance-specific + secret config
**/*.pem
**/*.key

# --- Python ---
